---

<BaseLayout title={meta.title} description={meta.description}>
  <main>
    <section class="hero bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-900 to-blue-700 text-white py-20">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">HOA & Condominium Property Services in Wilmette, IL</h1>
        <p class="text-xl mb-8 max-w-3xl">Professional property services for HOA and condominium associations in one of the North Shore's most vibrant communities.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="prose max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Vector Building Services is proud to serve HOA and condominium associations in Wilmette, Illinois, one of the North Shore's most vibrant and historic communities. With its classic lakefront estates, tree-lined neighborhoods, and active condo communities west of Green Bay Road, Wilmette associations rely on us for maintenance, landscaping, snow removal, and contracting solutions that preserve property value and enhance resident satisfaction.
          </p>

          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
            Whether your property is near Gillson Park, tucked within the downtown Wilmette shops, or part of a suburban HOA campus, our team delivers responsive, professional services tailored to your community's needs.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-blue-900">Why Wilmette Associations Partner with Vector</h2>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
              <h3 class="font-bold text-blue-700 mb-2">Local North Shore Expertise</h3>
              <p>We know the unique property challenges Wilmette faces, from lakefront storms to large-scale landscaping.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
              <h3 class="font-bold text-blue-700 mb-2">Comprehensive Service</h3>
              <p>A single partner for maintenance, janitorial, seasonal, and contracting.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
              <h3 class="font-bold text-blue-700 mb-2">24/7 Emergency Response</h3>
              <p>Always on call during snowstorms, floods, or urgent repairs.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
              <h3 class="font-bold text-blue-700 mb-2">Board-Friendly Approach</h3>
              <p>Clear communication, transparent pricing, and preventive planning.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-blue-900">Interior Services for Wilmette Communities</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">HOA and condo boards trust us to maintain and improve shared interior spaces, including:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Lobby and clubhouse upgrades</li>
            <li>Fitness center and amenity renovations</li>
            <li>Common-area janitorial programs</li>
            <li>Lighting system retrofits</li>
            <li>Routine plumbing and electrical maintenance</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mb-8">From historic condo buildings near Sheridan Road to newer developments inland, we keep interiors safe, functional, and welcoming.</p>

          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-blue-900">Exterior Services in Wilmette</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">The North Shore's seasonal weather can quickly wear down building exteriors. Our team provides:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Roofing and siding repair or replacement</li>
            <li>Masonry and tuckpointing for Wilmette's many brick buildings</li>
            <li>Drainage and water-control systems</li>
            <li>Parking lot sealing, striping, and repairs</li>
            <li>Entryway and exterior lighting upkeep</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mb-8">We focus on preventive maintenance to protect associations from costly assessments.</p>

          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-blue-900">Seasonal Services</h2>

          <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg mb-6">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-blue-800">24/7 Snow & Ice Removal</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>Per-push service or seasonal agreements available</li>
              <li>Parking lots, driveways, and sidewalks kept clear</li>
              <li>Salting and de-icing for resident and guest safety</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-green-50 p-6 rounded-lg mb-6">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-green-800">Landscaping (April 1 ‚Äì October 31)</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>Weekly lawn mowing and trimming</li>
              <li>Seasonal flower and shrub planting</li>
              <li>Mulching, fertilization, and aeration</li>
              <li>Leaf removal and fall cleanup</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-orange-50 p-6 rounded-lg mb-8">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-orange-800">Storm & Flood Response</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>Emergency water pumping</li>
              <li>Clearing branches and debris after summer storms</li>
              <li>Drain inspections to prevent backups</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-blue-900">Serving Wilmette & Nearby Communities</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">In addition to Wilmette, Vector proudly supports associations in:</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mb-8">
            <a href="/locations/suburbs/evanston" class="bg-blue-100 hover:bg-blue-200 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg transition">Evanston</a>
            <a href="/locations/suburbs/winnetka" class="bg-blue-100 hover:bg-blue-200 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg transition">Winnetka</a>
            <a href="/locations/suburbs/kenilworth" class="bg-blue-100 hover:bg-blue-200 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg transition">Kenilworth</a>
          </div>

          <div class="text-center mb-12">
            <a href="/locations/suburbs" class="inline-block bg-gray-200 hover:bg-gray-300 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold transition">‚Üê Back to Suburbs Hub</a>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-blue-900 text-white p-8 rounded-lg text-center">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Partner with Vector in Wilmette</h2>
            <p class="mb-6 text-lg">
              Wilmette associations deserve a partner who understands North Shore living. At Vector Building Services, we provide customized, reliable property services for HOA and condominium boards, backed by 24/7 support and local expertise.
